{"tid":1296566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「這是中國所懼怕的」 WSJ：新示威改以大陸人為對象","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:50:42.000Z","uid":153236,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71bbee23d883a1f1de69a0d0666a7d5757fb0708","tid":1296566,"uid":153236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"香港「反送中」運動的戰線周日由港島延至九龍尖沙嘴，《華爾街日報》（WSJ）網站周日頭條報道，題為《香港最新一輪示威以不同的一群為對象：中國大陸人》（Latest Hong Kong Protest Plays to a Different Crowd: Mainland Chinese）。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，周日的23萬人遊行是香港一個月內第四次大型示威。遊行所經地點盡是內地遊客常到的地區，以尖沙嘴梳士巴利花園為起點，經九龍公園徑，在尖沙嘴消防局進入廣東道，以執行「一地兩檢」的高鐵西九龍站為終點。<br />\n<br />\n遊行主辦者給《WSJ》的訊息寫道：「選擇這條遊行路線，是要引起大陸人關注（示威），而這是中國所懼怕的」。報道指一向審查敏感新聞的中國，試圖不「積極介入」香港近期的集會和衝突，但對內地司法制度黑箱作業的憂慮，正是對港府強推「逃犯條例」大聲疾呼的根本原因。<br />\n<br />\n參與遊行的17歲姓劉學生向《WSJ》表示，「希望他們知道真相，在內地傳播消息。」32歲姓黃內地遊客說：「我明白為何他們不想修訂《逃犯條例》，但我不支持任何形式的暴力。」黃又說：「我在內地的朋友不明白為何有人會反對此例。他們認為十分正常。」<br />\n<br />\n28歲遊行參與者Gladis Au提及湖北武漢陽邏民眾連日來為抗議興建垃圾焚燒發電廠而上街。她說：「中國公安毆打示威者，『河蟹』訊息&hellip;&hellip;我認為我們今天要出來，否則我們有一天會變成武漢。」<br />\n<br />\n報道指，認為北京此時會自毀國際形象，在港秋後算賬的人不多，但當年輕的社運人士衡量運動的新方案之同時，舊日記憶又再浮現。<br />\n<br />\n1989年為法新社採訪六四事件的泛民立法會議員毛孟靜向WSJ說：「我七一當晚感到萬分驚恐，因為我聽到年輕人在立法會外討論，說『我們要留下，幫手保護進入大樓內的人，我們的人數要多過警察』&hellip;&hellip;這些對白我30年前在天安門聽過。」<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190708/59799617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59799617&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpWCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=a31f8bf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59799617&h=3584d638\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190708/59799617</a>"},{"pid":"bf0b38f86265ce6f993eddbe2082852a1b9c07bf","tid":1296566,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bbcf84846342bc740275143bfb1550f8c50583","tid":1296566,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a1f061b3d8920d6ae550c1f7abdb7b5c2ca1df","tid":1296566,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"呢個邊戰線一定要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ca385f313561e5cc85f4c7cd817fc1c9977426","tid":1296566,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c09196a657acc487269a3c8f7a65bc19564d3d32","tid":1296566,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:44:18.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"41e975593c8a862dace4f3454efcc40f469ac385","tid":1296566,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62818c2c61cb5005c50d6d108b0dde6c0d417889","tid":1296566,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e975593c8a862dace4f3454efcc40f469ac385","tid":1296566,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor